cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper discusses deep learning techniques for learning a common representation for multi-view data, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM). Given that the paper proposes a novel deep autoencoder-based method for multi-modal data, it is most likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.MM.
